          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
          Back to Blog
        </a>
        <span class="section-label-light">Hiring a Contractor</span>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-6 leading-tight">How to Choose a General Contractor in Utah<br/><span style="color: var(--color-cyan)">(Without Getting Burned)</span></h1>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6)">
          <span>By Jared Bayless</span>
          <span>·</span>
          <span>November 12, 2025</span>
          <span>·</span>
          <span>8 min read</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
